e:[["$","title","0",{"children":"How to Identify Risk Controls in ISO 9001 | ISO 9001 QMS Risk Controls | Wizms"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Assessing risks in ISO 9001 Quality Management System and devising risk controls is a significant part of risk-based thinking for exemplary management system."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"risk controls in ISO 9001, ISO 9001 requirements, ISO 9001 certification in Dubai, how to get ISO 9001 certification in Dubai, ISO 9001 certification in UAE, benefits of ISO 9001 certification, ISO 9001 consultants."}],["$","meta","3",{"property":"og:title","content":"How to Identify Risk Controls in ISO 9001 | ISO 9001 QMS Risk Controls | Wizms"}],["$","meta","4",{"property":"og:description","content":"Assessing risks in ISO 9001 Quality Management System and devising risk controls is a significant part of risk-based thinking for exemplary management system."}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://wizms.net/how-to-identify-risk-controls-in-iso-9001"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:type","content":"article"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"article:published_time","content":"2026-01-02T06:31:37+00:00"}],["$","meta","8",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary"}],["$","meta","9",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"How to Identify Risk Controls in ISO 9001 | ISO 9001 QMS Risk Controls | Wizms"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Assessing risks in ISO 9001 Quality Management System and devising risk controls is a significant part of risk-based thinking for exemplary management system."}],["$","link","11",{"rel":"icon","href":"/favicon.ico"}],["$","$L1b","12",{}]]
10:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Avoiding risk:"}]
11:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"For significant risks, you will have to value more highly to take action to hinder the risk from happening, or in other words: modify the possibility of occurrence of those risks. This might be enhancement in the existing process or replacing existing instruments or equipment with much better equipment, or dynamic style of approach to get rid of those parts that are inflicting the risks. The secret is that when the risk control actions are completed, the risk will no longer be existing."}]
12:["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Eliminating the source of risks:"}]
13:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"One efficient technique of avoiding the risk is to eliminate the risk source. This could involve implementing modifications to the parts employed in an assembly or removing a process step that's risky and replacing it with one that doesn't have the chance for any kinds of risk."}]
14:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Sharing the risk:"}]
15:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Typically, you should be able to transfer a risk elsewhere, corresponding to implementing a process carried out by the skilled supplier or professional instead of doing it yourself. One other different way of transferring risk is through having insurance in house that will offer the required additional resources to cope up with the persisting problem or issue if it happens."}]
16:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Changing the probability of risk consequences:"}]
17:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Setting up administrative training, controls and regular or periodic inspections can effectively and efficiently mitigate the probability of the risk occurrence. This ensures that you will stop the risk from happening, but you are effectively enhancing the possibilities of identifying the risk when it happens. This mitigation typically includes devising contingency plans in the house to take care of the implications of the risk once the issue has occurred. These plans will embrace such things as remodelling product or procedures to modify a process to an orthodox state. If the risk still exists, now you have got actions and plans to cut back the possibility of risk consequences."}]
18:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Taking the risk to pursue an opportunity:"}]
19:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"We have often mentioned about risks in terms of having a negative consequence, but what if taking a risk turns out to be an opportunity for your organization or company? In these kinds of situations, you're assessing the risk in terms of betterment of your organization which in turn you're just maximizing the opportunities and taking action to create it and make it happen. When you accomplish this effectively, you're exploiting the risks so as to get benefitted by actions in the long run of your organization."}]
